<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #2c5aa0; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .info-box { background-color: white; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #2c5aa0; }
        .password-box { background-color: #f0f4ff; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; border: 2px solid #2c5aa0; }
        .password { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #2c5aa0; letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
        .highlight { color: #2c5aa0; font-weight: bold; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #2c5aa0; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; }
        .warning { background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to EmpCon Chicko Chicken</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong>{{employeeName}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Your EmpCon Chicko Chicken account has been created successfully. Below is your temporary password to access the system.</p>

            <div class="password-box">
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">Your Temporary Password</p>
                <p class="password">{{tempPassword}}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="warning">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">‚ö†Ô∏è Important Security Notice</h3>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>This is a <strong>temporary password</strong> that expires in <strong>24 hours</strong></li>
                    <li>You will be required to change this password on first login</li>
                    <li>Never share your password with anyone</li>
                    <li>If you did not expect this email, please contact your administrator immediately</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>üìã Next Steps</h3>
                <ol style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Click the button below to access the login page</li>
                    <li>Enter your email and the temporary password above</li>
                    <li>You will be prompted to create a new secure password</li>
                    <li>Complete the password change to access your dashboard</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Login</a>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>üîí Password Requirements</h3>
                <p>When creating your new password, please ensure it meets the following criteria:</p>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>At least 8 characters long</li>
                    <li>Contains at least one uppercase letter</li>
                    <li>Contains at least one lowercase letter</li>
                    <li>Contains at least one number</li>
                    <li>Contains at least one special character</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact your system administrator.</p>
            <p><strong>EmpCon Chicko Chicken Management System</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was automatically sent by the EmpCon Chicko Chicken Employee Management System.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact the system administrator.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>